ps://baomoi-static.bmcdn.me/web/styles/img/logo-baomoi-gray.png\u0027)] after:bg-[length:20%_auto] after:bg-[position:center_50%] after:bg-no-repeat after:bg-[#e9ecef]\"\u003e\n   \u003ci class\u003d\"icon font-[\u0027bm-font-icon\u0027] not-italic font-normal normal-case leading-none antialiased [speak:never] [font-variant:normal] ic-search-plus w-[44px] h-[44px] flex items-center justify-center absolute right-[5px] top-[5px] z-[2] text-white rounded-full cursor-pointer bg-[rgba(0,0,0,0.5)] hover:bg-[var(--primary)]\"\u003e\u003c/i\u003e\n   \u003cbutton class\u003d\"image lazy-image overflow-hidden photo block leading-[0] cursor-pointer text-center opacity-0\" style\u003d\"width:625px;height:350px\"\u003e\n    \u003cpicture\u003e\n     \u003csource srcset\u003d\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw\u003d\u003d\" type\u003d\"image/avif\"\u003e\u003c/source\u003e\n     \u003csource srcset\u003d\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw\u003d\u003d\" type\u003d\"image/webp\"\u003e\u003c/source\u003e\n     \u003cimg src\u003d\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw\u003d\u003d\" alt\u003d\"Tổng thống Nga Vladimir Putin\" width\u003d\"625\" height\u003d\"350\" /\u003e\n    \u003c/picture\u003e\u003c/button\u003e\n  \u003c/div\u003e\n  \u003cp class\u003d\"text media-caption text-center text-[18px] leading-[24px]\"\u003e\u003cem\u003eTổng thống Nga Vladimir Putin\u003c/em\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n  \u003cp class\u003d\"text\"\u003eTổng thống \u003ca class\u003d\"tag-link\" href\u003d\"/vladimir-putin-tag87.epi\"\u003ePutin\u003c/a\u003e cho biết: “Tất nhi\u0026ecirc;n, đ\u0026acirc;y l\u0026agrave; một h\u0026agrave;nh động kh\u0026ocirc;ng th\u0026acirc;n thiện đối với Nga. Đ\u0026acirc;y l\u0026agrave; điều hiển nhi\u0026ecirc;n, v\u0026agrave; điều n\u0026agrave;y kh\u0026ocirc;ng củng cố quan hệ Nga - Mỹ, vốn mới chỉ bắt đầu phục hồi”.\u003c/p\u003e\n  \u003cp class\u003d\"text\"\u003eNh\u0026agrave; l\u0026atilde;nh đạo \u003ca class\u003d\"tag-link\" href\u003d\"/lien-bang-nga-tag117.epi\"\u003eNga\u003c/a\u003e n\u0026oacute;i th\u0026ecirc;m rằng c\u0026aacute;c lệnh trừng phạt mới sẽ kh\u0026ocirc;ng ảnh hưởng đ\u0026aacute;ng kể đến t\u0026igrave;nh h\u0026igrave;nh kinh tế của Nga. Tuy nhi\u0026ecirc;n, \u0026ocirc;ng nhắc lại \u0026yacute; định tiếp tục tiến h\u0026agrave;nh đ\u0026agrave;m ph\u0026aacute;n với Tổng thống Trump, n\u0026oacute;i rằng đối thoại lu\u0026ocirc;n tốt hơn đối đầu hoặc chiến tranh.\u003c/p\u003e\n  \u003cp class\u003d\"text\"\u003eTrước đ\u0026oacute;, \u003ca class\u003d\"tag-link\" href\u003d\"/my-tag81.epi\"\u003eBộ T\u0026agrave;i ch\u0026iacute;nh Mỹ\u003c/a\u003e c\u0026ocirc;ng bố c\u0026aacute;c lệnh trừng phạt bổ sung đối với Nga, với l\u0026yacute; do “Nga thiếu cam kết nghi\u0026ecirc;m t\u0026uacute;c đối với một tiến tr\u0026igrave;nh h\u0026ograve;a b\u0026igrave;nh”. C\u0026aacute;c lệnh trừng phạt nhắm v\u0026agrave;o hai c\u0026ocirc;ng ty dầu mỏ lớn nhất của Nga l\u0026agrave; Rosneft v\u0026agrave; Lukoil, cũng như c\u0026aacute;c c\u0026ocirc;ng ty con của họ.\u003c/p\u003e\n  \u003cp class\u003d\"text\"\u003eTổng thống Ukraine \u003ca class\u003d\"tag-link\" href\u003d\"/volodymyr-zelensky-tag11698.epi\"\u003eVolodymyr Zelensky\u003c/a\u003e hoan ngh\u0026ecirc;nh c\u0026aacute;c lệnh trừng phạt. \u0026Ocirc;ng nhắc lại quan điểm rằng gia tăng \u0026aacute;p lực l\u0026ecirc;n Nga sẽ mang lại đ\u0026agrave;m ph\u0026aacute;n v\u0026agrave; thậm ch\u0026iacute; l\u0026agrave; một kế hoạch h\u0026ograve;a b\u0026igrave;nh khả thi.\u003c/p\u003e\n  \u003cp class\u003d\"text\"\u003e\u0026Ocirc;ng Zelensky cho biết: “Kế hoạch h\u0026ograve;a b\u0026igrave;nh bắt đầu từ lệnh ngừng bắn. Nhưng nếu kh\u0026ocirc;ng thể ngừng bắn, th\u0026igrave; cũng c\u0026oacute; thể bắt đầu bằng \u0026yacute; định ngồi lại v\u0026agrave; n\u0026oacute;i chuyện với nhau”.\u003c/p\u003e\n  \u003cp class\u003d\"text body-author text-right\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eTheo NHK\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n  \u003cp class\u003d\"text body-author text-right\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eMai Phương\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n  \u003cp class\u003d\"text body-author text-right\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eTheo NHK\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n \u003c/div\u003e\n \u003cdiv class\u003d\"pswp\" tabindex\u003d\"-1\" role\u003d\"dialog\" aria-hidden\u003d\"true\"\u003e\n  \u003cdiv class\u003d\"pswp__bg\"\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n  \u003cdiv class\u003d\"pswp__scroll-wrap\"\u003e\n   \u003cdiv class\u003d\"pswp__container\"\u003e\n    \u003cdiv class\u003d\"pswp__item\"\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n    \u003cdiv class\u003d\"pswp__item\"\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n    \u003cdiv class\u003d\"pswp__item\"\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n   \u003c/div\u003e\n   \u003cdiv class\u003d\"pswp__ui pswp__ui--hidden\"\u003e\n    \u003cdiv class\u003d\"pswp__top-bar\"\u003e\n     \u003cdiv class\u003d\"pswp__counter\"\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n     \u003cbutton type\u003d\"button\" class\u003d\"pswp__button pswp__button--close\" title\u003d\"Close (Esc)\"\u003e\u003c/button\u003e\n     \u003cbutton type\u003d\"button\" class\u003d\"pswp__button pswp__button--share\" title\u003d\"Share\"\u003e\u003c/button\u003e\n     \u003cbutton type\u003d\"button\" class\u003d\"pswp__button pswp__button--fs\" title\u003d\"Toggle fullscreen\"\u003e\u003c/button\u003e\n     \u003cbutton type\u003d\"button\" class\u003d\"pswp__button pswp__button--zoom\" title\u003d\"Zoom in/out\"\u003e\u003c/button\u003e\n     \u003cdiv class\u003d\"pswp__preloader\"\u003e\n      \u003cdiv class\u003d\"pswp__preloader__icn\"\u003e\n       \u003cdiv class\u003d\"pswp__preloader__cut\"\u003e\n        \u003cdiv class\u003d\"pswp__preloader__donut\"\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n       \u003c/div\u003e\n      \u003c/div\u003e\n     \u003c/div\u003e\n    \u003c/div\u003e\n    \u003cdiv class\u003d\"pswp__share-modal pswp__sh